<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200905/89e0f18a31284ae9a9161fa3c61c13d1.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">热搜又爆了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">《乘风破浪的姐姐》最后一期，7人团「出道」了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">大家最关心的成团名单，有意料之外，也有情理之中。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200905/6a0eb80758d74fcd9af31bf817793878.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
